

### 5. Heroku Deployment Button Setup
To enable the one-click deployment via Heroku, follow these steps:
1. Create a app.json file in the root of your GitHub repository:

`json
{
  "name": "Jujutsu Kaisen Telegram Bot",
  "description": "A bot for Jujutsu Kaisen character battles and quotes.",
  "repository": "https://github.com/vip-rehan-mail/JJk-waifu-Game",
  "keywords": ["python", "telegram", "bot"],
  "env": {
    "TOKEN": {
      "description": "The bot token from BotFather",
      "required": true
    }
  },
  "buildpacks": [
    {
      "url": "heroku/python"
    }
  ]
}
